{
  "taskId": "task_1778152228858_5",
  "requestedModel": "anti-claude-opus-4.6-thinking",
  "text": "### 1. 환경변수 설정\n\n`.env` 파일을 생성하여 JWT 시크릿 키를 정의합니다. 이 키는 토큰 서명에 사용되며, 외부에 노출되어서는 안 됩니다.\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \".env\",\n    \"content\": \"JWT_SECRET=MyCrewSecretKeyForDevelopmentPurposeOnlyChangeInProduction\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n\n```.env\nJWT_SECRET=MyCrewSecretKeyForDevelopmentPurposeOnlyChangeInProduction\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. User 모듈 구현\n\n사용자 정보를 관리하는 핵심 모듈입니다.\n\n#### 2.1. User Entity (`src/user/entities/user.entity.ts`)\n\n데이터베이스 `users` 테이블과 매핑되는 `User` 엔티티를 정의합니다. 사용자 타입(광고주/매체주)을 관리하기 위한 `enum`을 포함하고, 데이터 저장 전 비밀번호를 자동으로 해싱하는 로직을 추가합니다.\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/user/entities/user.entity.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Entity, PrimaryGeneratedColumn, Column, CreateDateColumn, UpdateDateColumn, BeforeInsert } from 'typeorm';\\nimport * as bcrypt from 'bcrypt';\\n\\nexport enum UserType {\\n  ADVERTISER = 'ADVERTISER',\\n  MEDIA_OWNER = 'MEDIA_OWNER',\\n}\\n\\n@Entity('users')\\nexport class User {\\n  @PrimaryGeneratedColumn('uuid')\\n  id: string;\\n\\n  @Column({ unique: true })\\n  email: string;\\n\\n  @Column()\\n  password: string;\\n\\n  @Column({\\n    type: 'enum',\\n    enum: UserType,\\n  })\\n  userType: UserType;\\n\\n  @CreateDateColumn()\\n  createdAt: Date;\\n\\n  @UpdateDateColumn()\\n  updatedAt: Date;\\n\\n  @BeforeInsert()\\n  async hashPassword() {\\n    this.password = await bcrypt.hash(this.password, 10);\\n  }\\n}\\n\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n\n```typescript\n// src/user/entities/user.entity.ts\nimport { Entity, PrimaryGeneratedColumn, Column, CreateDateColumn, UpdateDateColumn, BeforeInsert } from 'typeorm';\nimport * as bcrypt from 'bcrypt';\n\nexport enum UserType {\n  ADVERTISER = 'ADVERTISER',\n  MEDIA_OWNER = 'MEDIA_OWNER',\n}\n\n@Entity('users')\nexport class User {\n  @PrimaryGeneratedColumn('uuid')\n  id: string;\n\n  @Column({ unique: true })\n  email: string;\n\n  @Column()\n  password: string;\n\n  @Column({\n    type: 'enum',\n    enum: UserType,\n  })\n  userType: UserType;\n\n  @CreateDateColumn()\n  createdAt: Date;\n\n  @UpdateDateColumn()\n  updatedAt: Date;\n\n  @BeforeInsert()\n  async hashPassword() {\n    this.password = await bcrypt.hash(this.password, 10);\n  }\n}\n```\n\n#### 2.2. User Service (`src/user/user.service.ts`)\n\n사용자 데이터 처리를 위한 비즈니스 로직을 담당합니다.\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/user/user.service.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Injectable, ConflictException } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { InjectRepository } from '@nestjs/typeorm';\\nimport { Repository } from 'typeorm';\\nimport { User } from './entities/user.entity';\\nimport { CreateUserDto } from './dto/create-user.dto';\\n\\n@Injectable()\\nexport class UserService {\\n  constructor(\\n    @InjectRepository(User)\\n    private readonly userRepository: Repository<User>,\\n  ) {}\\n\\n  async create(createUserDto: CreateUserDto): Promise<Omit<User, 'password'>> {\\n    const existingUser = await this.userRepository.findOne({ where: { email: createUserDto.email } });\\n    if (existingUser) {\\n      throw new ConflictException('이미 사용중인 이메일입니다.');\\n    }\\n\\n    const user = this.userRepository.create(createUserDto);\\n    const savedUser = await this.userRepository.save(user);\\n\\n    // eslint-disable-next-line @typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars\\n    const { password, ...result } = savedUser;\\n    return result;\\n  }\\n\\n  async findOneByEmail(email: string): Promise<User | undefined> {\\n    return this.userRepository.findOne({ where: { email } });\\n  }\\n\\n  async findOneById(id: string): Promise<User | undefined> {\\n    return this.userRepository.findOne({ where: { id } });\\n  }\\n}\\n\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n\n```typescript\n// src/user/user.service.ts\nimport { Injectable, ConflictException } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { InjectRepository } from '@nestjs/typeorm';\nimport { Repository } from 'typeorm';\nimport { User } from './entities/user.entity';\nimport { CreateUserDto } from './dto/create-user.dto';\n\n@Injectable()\nexport class UserService {\n  constructor(\n    @InjectRepository(User)\n    private readonly userRepository: Repository<User>,\n  ) {}\n\n  async create(createUserDto: CreateUserDto): Promise<Omit<User, 'password'>> {\n    const existingUser = await this.userRepository.findOne({ where: { email: createUserDto.email } });\n    if (existingUser) {\n      throw new ConflictException('이미 사용중인 이메일입니다.');\n    }\n\n    const user = this.userRepository.create(createUserDto);\n    const savedUser = await this.userRepository.save(user);\n\n    // eslint-disable-next-line @typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars\n    const { password, ...result } = savedUser;\n    return result;\n  }\n\n  async findOneByEmail(email: string): Promise<User | undefined> {\n    return this.userRepository.findOne({ where: { email } });\n  }\n\n  async findOneById(id: string): Promise<User | undefined> {\n    return this.userRepository.findOne({ where: { id } });\n  }\n}\n```\n\n#### 2.3. User Module (`src/user/user.module.ts`)\n\n`User` 모듈의 구성 요소들을 등록하고 `UserService`를 다른 모듈에서 사용할 수 있도록 `exports` 합니다.\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/user/user.module.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Module } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { TypeOrmModule } from '@nestjs/typeorm';\\nimport { UserService } from './user.service';\\nimport { UserController } from './user.controller';\\nimport { User } from './entities/user.entity';\\n\\n@Module({\\n  imports: [TypeOrmModule.forFeature([User])],\\n  providers: [UserService],\\n  controllers: [UserController],\\n  exports: [UserService], // AuthService에서 사용하기 위해 export\\n})\\nexport class UserModule {}\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/user/user.controller.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Controller, Get, UseGuards, Request } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { JwtAuthGuard } from '../auth/guards/jwt-auth.guard';\\n\\n@Controller('users')\\nexport class UserController {\\n    // 예시: 인증된 사용자만 자신의 프로필 정보를 조회하는 API\\n    @UseGuards(JwtAuthGuard)\\n    @Get('profile')\\n    getProfile(@Request() req) {\\n        // JwtAuthGuard를 통과하면 req.user에 토큰 페이로드(사용자 정보)가 담겨 있음\\n        return req.user;\\n    }\\n}\\n\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n\n```typescript\n// src/user/user.module.ts\nimport { Module } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { TypeOrmModule } from '@nestjs/typeorm';\nimport { UserService } from './user.service';\nimport { UserController } from './user.controller';\nimport { User } from './entities/user.entity';\n\n@Module({\n  imports: [TypeOrmModule.forFeature([User])],\n  providers: [UserService],\n  controllers: [UserController],\n  exports: [UserService], // AuthService에서 사용하기 위해 export\n})\nexport class UserModule {}\n```\n\n```typescript\n// src/user/user.controller.ts\nimport { Controller, Get, UseGuards, Request } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { JwtAuthGuard } from '../auth/guards/jwt-auth.guard';\n\n@Controller('users')\nexport class UserController {\n    // 예시: 인증된 사용자만 자신의 프로필 정보를 조회하는 API\n    @UseGuards(JwtAuthGuard)\n    @Get('profile')\n    getProfile(@Request() req) {\n        // JwtAuthGuard를 통과하면 req.user에 토큰 페이로드(사용자 정보)가 담겨 있음\n        return req.user;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Auth 모듈 구현\n\n회원가입, 로그인 등 인증 관련 기능을 총괄하는 모듈입니다.\n\n#### 3.1. DTO 및 Passport 전략 (`src/auth/...`)\n\nAPI 요청 데이터를 검증하기 위한 DTO와 Passport 인증 전략(Local, JWT)을 정의합니다.\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/user/dto/create-user.dto.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { IsEmail, IsString, IsNotEmpty, MinLength, IsEnum } from 'class-validator';\\nimport { UserType } from '../entities/user.entity';\\n\\nexport class CreateUserDto {\\n  @IsEmail()\\n  @IsNotEmpty()\\n  email: string;\\n\\n  @IsString()\\n  @IsNotEmpty()\\n  @MinLength(8)\\n  password: string;\\n\\n  @IsEnum(UserType)\\n  @IsNotEmpty()\\n  userType: UserType;\\n}\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/auth/strategies/local.strategy.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Strategy } from 'passport-local';\\nimport { PassportStrategy } from '@nestjs/passport';\\nimport { Injectable, UnauthorizedException } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { AuthService } from '../auth.service';\\n\\n@Injectable()\\nexport class LocalStrategy extends PassportStrategy(Strategy) {\\n  constructor(private authService: AuthService) {\\n    super({ usernameField: 'email' }); // 기본 'username'을 'email'로 오버라이드\\n  }\\n\\n  async validate(email: string, pass: string): Promise<any> {\\n    const user = await this.authService.validateUser(email, pass);\\n    if (!user) {\\n      throw new UnauthorizedException('이메일 또는 비밀번호가 올바르지 않습니다.');\\n    }\\n    return user;\\n  }\\n}\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/auth/strategies/jwt.strategy.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { ExtractJwt, Strategy } from 'passport-jwt';\\nimport { PassportStrategy } from '@nestjs/passport';\\nimport { Injectable } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { ConfigService } from '@nestjs/config';\\n\\n@Injectable()\\nexport class JwtStrategy extends PassportStrategy(Strategy) {\\n  constructor(private readonly configService: ConfigService) {\\n    super({\\n      jwtFromRequest: ExtractJwt.fromAuthHeaderAsBearerToken(),\\n      ignoreExpiration: false,\\n      secretOrKey: configService.get<string>('JWT_SECRET'),\\n    });\\n  }\\n\\n  async validate(payload: any) {\\n    // 토큰이 유효하면 payload를 반환\\n    // NestJS가 이 값을 req.user에 첨부함\\n    return { userId: payload.sub, email: payload.email, userType: payload.userType };\\n  }\\n}\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/auth/guards/jwt-auth.guard.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Injectable } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { AuthGuard } from '@nestjs/passport';\\n\\n@Injectable()\\nexport class JwtAuthGuard extends AuthGuard('jwt') {}\\n\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n\n```typescript\n// src/user/dto/create-user.dto.ts\nimport { IsEmail, IsString, IsNotEmpty, MinLength, IsEnum } from 'class-validator';\nimport { UserType } from '../entities/user.entity';\n\nexport class CreateUserDto {\n  @IsEmail()\n  @IsNotEmpty()\n  email: string;\n\n  @IsString()\n  @IsNotEmpty()\n  @MinLength(8)\n  password: string;\n\n  @IsEnum(UserType)\n  @IsNotEmpty()\n  userType: UserType;\n}\n```\n\n```typescript\n// src/auth/strategies/local.strategy.ts\nimport { Strategy } from 'passport-local';\nimport { PassportStrategy } from '@nestjs/passport';\nimport { Injectable, UnauthorizedException } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { AuthService } from '../auth.service';\n\n@Injectable()\nexport class LocalStrategy extends PassportStrategy(Strategy) {\n  constructor(private authService: AuthService) {\n    super({ usernameField: 'email' }); // 기본 'username'을 'email'로 오버라이드\n  }\n\n  async validate(email: string, pass: string): Promise<any> {\n    const user = await this.authService.validateUser(email, pass);\n    if (!user) {\n      throw new UnauthorizedException('이메일 또는 비밀번호가 올바르지 않습니다.');\n    }\n    return user;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n```typescript\n// src/auth/strategies/jwt.strategy.ts\nimport { ExtractJwt, Strategy } from 'passport-jwt';\nimport { PassportStrategy } from '@nestjs/passport';\nimport { Injectable } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { ConfigService } from '@nestjs/config';\n\n@Injectable()\nexport class JwtStrategy extends PassportStrategy(Strategy) {\n  constructor(private readonly configService: ConfigService) {\n    super({\n      jwtFromRequest: ExtractJwt.fromAuthHeaderAsBearerToken(),\n      ignoreExpiration: false,\n      secretOrKey: configService.get<string>('JWT_SECRET'),\n    });\n  }\n\n  async validate(payload: any) {\n    // 토큰이 유효하면 payload를 반환\n    // NestJS가 이 값을 req.user에 첨부함\n    return { userId: payload.sub, email: payload.email, userType: payload.userType };\n  }\n}\n```\n\n```typescript\n// src/auth/guards/jwt-auth.guard.ts\nimport { Injectable } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { AuthGuard } from '@nestjs/passport';\n\n@Injectable()\nexport class JwtAuthGuard extends AuthGuard('jwt') {}\n```\n\n#### 3.2. Auth Service (`src/auth/auth.service.ts`)\n\n인증 관련 핵심 비즈니스 로직입니다. 사용자 검증, JWT 생성, 회원가입 처리를 담당합니다.\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/auth/auth.service.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Injectable } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { UserService } from '../user/user.service';\\nimport { JwtService } from '@nestjs/jwt';\\nimport * as bcrypt from 'bcrypt';\\nimport { CreateUserDto } from 'src/user/dto/create-user.dto';\\nimport { User } from 'src/user/entities/user.entity';\\n\\n@Injectable()\\nexport class AuthService {\\n  constructor(\\n    private readonly userService: UserService,\\n    private readonly jwtService: JwtService,\\n  ) {}\\n\\n  async validateUser(email: string, pass: string): Promise<any> {\\n    const user = await this.userService.findOneByEmail(email);\\n    if (user && (await bcrypt.compare(pass, user.password))) {\\n      // eslint-disable-next-line @typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars\\n      const { password, ...result } = user;\\n      return result;\\n    }\\n    return null;\\n  }\\n\\n  async login(user: Omit<User, 'password'>) {\\n    const payload = { email: user.email, sub: user.id, userType: user.userType };\\n    return {\\n      accessToken: this.jwtService.sign(payload),\\n    };\\n  }\\n\\n  async register(createUserDto: CreateUserDto) {\\n    return this.userService.create(createUserDto);\\n  }\\n}\\n\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n\n```typescript\n// src/auth/auth.service.ts\nimport { Injectable } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { UserService } from '../user/user.service';\nimport { JwtService } from '@nestjs/jwt';\nimport * as bcrypt from 'bcrypt';\nimport { CreateUserDto } from 'src/user/dto/create-user.dto';\nimport { User } from 'src/user/entities/user.entity';\n\n@Injectable()\nexport class AuthService {\n  constructor(\n    private readonly userService: UserService,\n    private readonly jwtService: JwtService,\n  ) {}\n\n  async validateUser(email: string, pass: string): Promise<any> {\n    const user = await this.userService.findOneByEmail(email);\n    if (user && (await bcrypt.compare(pass, user.password))) {\n      // eslint-disable-next-line @typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars\n      const { password, ...result } = user;\n      return result;\n    }\n    return null;\n  }\n\n  async login(user: Omit<User, 'password'>) {\n    const payload = { email: user.email, sub: user.id, userType: user.userType };\n    return {\n      accessToken: this.jwtService.sign(payload),\n    };\n  }\n\n  async register(createUserDto: CreateUserDto) {\n    return this.userService.create(createUserDto);\n  }\n}\n```\n\n#### 3.3. Auth Controller (`src/auth/auth.controller.ts`)\n\n`register`, `login` API 엔드포인트를 정의합니다.\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/auth/auth.controller.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Controller, Post, Body, UseGuards, Request } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { AuthService } from './auth.service';\\nimport { CreateUserDto } from '../user/dto/create-user.dto';\\nimport { LocalAuthGuard } from './guards/local-auth.guard';\\n\\n@Controller('auth')\\nexport class AuthController {\\n  constructor(private readonly authService: AuthService) {}\\n\\n  @Post('register')\\n  async register(@Body() createUserDto: CreateUserDto) {\\n    return this.authService.register(createUserDto);\\n  }\\n\\n  @UseGuards(LocalAuthGuard) // LocalStrategy를 실행\\n  @Post('login')\\n  async login(@Request() req) {\\n    // LocalAuthGuard가 성공하면 req.user에 사용자 정보가 담김\\n    return this.authService.login(req.user);\\n  }\\n}\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/auth/guards/local-auth.guard.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Injectable } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { AuthGuard } from '@nestjs/passport';\\n\\n@Injectable()\\nexport class LocalAuthGuard extends AuthGuard('local') {}\\n\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n\n```typescript\n// src/auth/auth.controller.ts\nimport { Controller, Post, Body, UseGuards, Request } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { AuthService } from './auth.service';\nimport { CreateUserDto } from '../user/dto/create-user.dto';\nimport { LocalAuthGuard } from './guards/local-auth.guard';\n\n@Controller('auth')\nexport class AuthController {\n  constructor(private readonly authService: AuthService) {}\n\n  @Post('register')\n  async register(@Body() createUserDto: CreateUserDto) {\n    return this.authService.register(createUserDto);\n  }\n\n  @UseGuards(LocalAuthGuard) // LocalStrategy를 실행\n  @Post('login')\n  async login(@Request() req) {\n    // LocalAuthGuard가 성공하면 req.user에 사용자 정보가 담김\n    return this.authService.login(req.user);\n  }\n}\n```\n\n```typescript\n// src/auth/guards/local-auth.guard.ts\nimport { Injectable } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { AuthGuard } from '@nestjs/passport';\n\n@Injectable()\nexport class LocalAuthGuard extends AuthGuard('local') {}\n```\n\n#### 3.4. Auth Module (`src/auth/auth.module.ts`)\n\n`Auth` 모듈의 구성 요소들을 등록하고, `JwtModule`을 `.env` 파일의 시크릿 키를 사용하여 비동기적으로 설정합니다.\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/auth/auth.module.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Module } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { AuthService } from './auth.service';\\nimport { AuthController } from './auth.controller';\\nimport { UserModule } from '../user/user.module';\\nimport { PassportModule } from '@nestjs/passport';\\nimport { JwtModule } from '@nestjs/jwt';\\nimport { ConfigModule, ConfigService } from '@nestjs/config';\\nimport { LocalStrategy } from './strategies/local.strategy';\\nimport { JwtStrategy } from './strategies/jwt.strategy';\\n\\n@Module({\\n  imports: [\\n    UserModule,\\n    PassportModule,\\n    ConfigModule, // ConfigService를 사용하기 위해 import\\n    JwtModule.registerAsync({\\n      imports: [ConfigModule],\\n      useFactory: async (configService: ConfigService) => ({\\n        secret: configService.get<string>('JWT_SECRET'),\\n        signOptions: { expiresIn: '1h' }, // 토큰 만료 시간 설정\\n      }),\\n      inject: [ConfigService],\\n    }),\\n  ],\\n  providers: [AuthService, LocalStrategy, JwtStrategy],\\n  controllers: [AuthController],\\n})\\nexport class AuthModule {}\\n\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n\n```typescript\n// src/auth/auth.module.ts\nimport { Module } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { AuthService } from './auth.service';\nimport { AuthController } from './auth.controller';\nimport { UserModule } from '../user/user.module';\nimport { PassportModule } from '@nestjs/passport';\nimport { JwtModule } from '@nestjs/jwt';\nimport { ConfigModule, ConfigService } from '@nestjs/config';\nimport { LocalStrategy } from './strategies/local.strategy';\nimport { JwtStrategy } from './strategies/jwt.strategy';\n\n@Module({\n  imports: [\n    UserModule,\n    PassportModule,\n    ConfigModule, // ConfigService를 사용하기 위해 import\n    JwtModule.registerAsync({\n      imports: [ConfigModule],\n      useFactory: async (configService: ConfigService) => ({\n        secret: configService.get<string>('JWT_SECRET'),\n        signOptions: { expiresIn: '1h' }, // 토큰 만료 시간 설정\n      }),\n      inject: [ConfigService],\n    }),\n  ],\n  providers: [AuthService, LocalStrategy, JwtStrategy],\n  controllers: [AuthController],\n})\nexport class AuthModule {}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. App 모듈 (`src/app.module.ts`)\n\n최상위 모듈에서 `ConfigModule`을 전역으로 설정하고, `UserModule`과 `AuthModule`을 등록합니다. 데이터베이스 연결 설정은 별도 `ormconfig.ts` 또는 `TypeOrmModule.forRootAsync`를 통해 이루어져야 합니다. (본 코드에서는 생략)\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/app.module.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Module } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { ConfigModule } from '@nestjs/config';\\nimport { TypeOrmModule } from '@nestjs/typeorm';\\nimport { AppController } from './app.controller';\\nimport { AppService } from './app.service';\\nimport { UserModule } from './user/user.module';\\nimport { AuthModule } from './auth/auth.module';\\n\\n@Module({\\n  imports: [\\n    ConfigModule.forRoot({\\n      isGlobal: true, // 모든 모듈에서 ConfigService 사용 가능\\n      envFilePath: '.env',\\n    }),\\n    // TypeOrmModule.forRootAsync(...) - DB 연결 설정 필요\\n    UserModule,\\n    AuthModule,\\n  ],\\n  controllers: [AppController],\\n  providers: [AppService],\\n})\\nexport class AppModule {}\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/app.controller.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Controller, Get } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { AppService } from './app.service';\\n\\",
  "processedBy": "ariDaemon-bridge (gemini-2.5-pro)",
  "timestamp": "2026-05-07T11:11:28.565Z"
}